00:07:47.980 --> 00:07:51.472
the psychic and somatic aspects of life energy,

157
00:07:51.472 --> 00:07:54.758
and he talks about the orgone energy.

158
00:07:54.758 --> 00:07:57.030
That these biolelectical currents he was measuring,

159
00:07:57.030 --> 00:08:00.325
Reich eventually came to appreciate this

160
