And this is hotly controversial,

163
00:08:08.923 --> 00:08:10.992
but there are aspects of it

164
00:08:10.992 --> 00:08:13.082
that have been verified time-and-again

165
00:08:13.082 --> 00:08:16.005
by different, classically-oriented researchers.

166
