00:08:44.124 --> 00:08:48.283
and his argumentation and the proofs that he gives

179
00:08:48.283 --> 00:08:51.825
later in his work, I think are quite exceptional,

180
00:08:51.825 --> 00:08:55.195
and nobody's ever really advanced significantly

181
00:08:55.195 --> 00:08:56.582
beyond them.

